{"tid":309774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史】有冇人對古代兵法有興趣？","createTime":"2017-07-05T10:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T07:46:05.000Z","uid":124991,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea57d18ff95ddd563da0f6839e192a35b99afd8","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"大家一齊討論下古代東西方嘅兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求教各位高人，有冇明朝之前嘅練兵、軍陣嘅兵書，唔想要《孫子兵法》嗰種睇完都唔會知點打仗嘅。"},{"pid":"531f594d70f860490d88323c965203091cbe472d","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:18:02.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎"},{"pid":"2bd66d46361e413b9aba266ad7266650d393d04b","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"冇人回嘅話我一係講住《紀效新書》先？"},{"pid":"ba839b074a6ec96977fc9fecc2b2167e4bbb2734","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sn3voly0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsn3voly0&h=27aaeff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以睇下呢個 講軍事編制<br />\n我都係之前略略睇過下<br />\n唔太記得"},{"pid":"52f1009d34381a80e6040f9b8f2d39213b65d8b9","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人回嘅話我一係講住《紀效新書》先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀"},{"pid":"11344ad11202e5b01faf30a5a3d009abc9c59c7a","tid":309774,"uid":41430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:20:41.000Z","msg":"想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如d一排過既盾陣可以集中一點攻擊之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlm"},{"pid":"5c0762c8b0663ee309c94d0ae9d8b2461256f26d","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\n有種講法係，《孫子兵法》裡面嘅佈陣、征練因為唔合時宜所以失傳咗，始終戰車喺漢初就完全失傳哂"},{"pid":"0246038b32a4fee46dcd150ea377c22e133b6a07","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\n有種講法係，《孫子兵法》裡面嘅佈陣、征練因為唔合時宜所以失傳咗，始終戰車喺漢初就完全失傳哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜孫子有講佈陣咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求詳細"},{"pid":"0dde8d7594983a298c1630b9924122db9a2e95bb","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如d一排過既盾陣可以集中一點攻擊之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlm</blockquote><br />\n羅馬盾陣嗰種？我淨係讀過下明朝兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古中國軍事技藝唔及西方，好少有同一個作戰單位之中用相同武器嘅兵陣（例如西班牙長槍陣），多數係使用唔同武器嘅（例如戚繼光嘅鴛鴦陣）。"},{"pid":"48e8694170a4ecde0ba60d75152e1d6505ed1593","tid":309774,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:31:38.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d8e7985cd7f12a5e8624cf694fe72dc8247bcc","tid":309774,"uid":90845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"直接睇戰史"},{"pid":"4cd5a3911dc3580b00e05638aa83eb1681a6c70e","tid":309774,"uid":61115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"由 古代 到 現代 都用既 斜線陣，<br />\n揚長避短，集中優勢/火力 包圍。"},{"pid":"039f74896821e701dd2208e25c495fa0de6403ec","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\n有種講法係，《孫子兵法》裡面嘅佈陣、征練因為唔合時宜所以失傳咗，始終戰車喺漢初就完全失傳哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜孫子有講佈陣咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求詳細</blockquote><br />\n冇，作為兵書嚟講好唔完整，所以有種講法係佢最初嘅兵陣內容因為後來不合時宜而失傳，有關先秦嘅兵陣可以睇下始皇陵兵馬俑嘅相關書藉，我記得有新中國（or中國大陸、中國內地、支那）歷史學家跟據始皇陵兵馬俑嘅考古所得寫過對秦兵陣嘅研究。但又有聞燕、魏已經有用騎兵作軍隊主力。唔熟先秦sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edba317ad97b81f3302b2b4c22cd5f289f78009f","tid":309774,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想知道方陣 矩陣果d點執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ff6f1919f58a3be1493972d8a3b3ed9bb35b56","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"出去食飯，返嚟講下〈比較武藝賞罰篇〉，我講得有錯嘅不吝賜教，小弟讀書少，應該有好多錯處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a5599d838b0bc8a89b7265dbe984b84e959b7c","tid":309774,"uid":70977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fe215f081a9236cdb75039d106e56ee1c52c8f8e","tid":309774,"uid":40862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"孔明八陣圖"},{"pid":"06a1c5e6231bf7bb116721fce0266b0673b1c75b","tid":309774,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"07dd75dbc06c44464252878030f3889f8ca2bdba","tid":309774,"uid":90845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\n有種講法係，《孫子兵法》裡面嘅佈陣、征練因為唔合時宜所以失傳咗，始終戰車喺漢初就完全失傳哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜孫子有講佈陣咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求詳細</blockquote><br />\n冇，作為兵書嚟講好唔完整，所以有種講法係佢最初嘅兵陣內容因為後來不合時宜而失傳，有關先秦嘅兵陣可以睇下始皇陵兵馬俑嘅相關書藉，我記得有新中國（or中國大陸、中國內地、支那）歷史學家跟據始皇陵兵馬俑嘅考古所得寫過對秦兵陣嘅研究。但又有聞燕、魏已經有用騎兵作軍隊主力。唔熟先秦sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n孫子成書於春秋末, 個陣未有騎兵作為一個兵種, 同期史書亦好少記載排陣。左傳記城濮之戰好似只有提及晉楚雙方左中右軍大約係咩。<br />\n<br />\n到戰國末, 六韜就開始有論述面對歩兵, 騎兵等應該點打。"},{"pid":"6567f911c9ce601bb68c216ae2c6f39ebf88d332","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\n有種講法係，《孫子兵法》裡面嘅佈陣、征練因為唔合時宜所以失傳咗，始終戰車喺漢初就完全失傳哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜孫子有講佈陣咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求詳細</blockquote><br />\n冇，作為兵書嚟講好唔完整，所以有種講法係佢最初嘅兵陣內容因為後來不合時宜而失傳，有關先秦嘅兵陣可以睇下始皇陵兵馬俑嘅相關書藉，我記得有新中國（or中國大陸、中國內地、支那）歷史學家跟據始皇陵兵馬俑嘅考古所得寫過對秦兵陣嘅研究。但又有聞燕、魏已經有用騎兵作軍隊主力。唔熟先秦sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n孫子成書於春秋末, 個陣未有騎兵作為一個兵種, 同期史書亦好少記載排陣。左傳記城濮之戰好似只有提及晉楚雙方左中右軍大約係咩。<br />\n<br />\n到戰國末, 六韜就開始有論述面對歩兵, 騎兵等應該點打。</blockquote><br />\n巴打啱，可以講下六韜？開post主要想學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f1e2140f1cf4e8ffd42dec4ee8c6c31b460128","tid":309774,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"個人認為孫子兵法其實甚具哲學味道"},{"pid":"3ef5338479a41c3d386f8ee3d3c2cb30327b882f","tid":309774,"uid":35538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人認為孫子兵法其實甚具哲學味道</blockquote><br />\n孫子兵法=戰略，但唔算多講戰術"},{"pid":"0559c9780b2d752fffe905c248757681b379054a","tid":309774,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二"},{"pid":"e2de756338f25f26514375bce0a47de365af323a","tid":309774,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"北宋年嘅兵法好多都有步對騎 集團作戰 陣圖之類<br />\n<br />\n守城 圍城 埋伏都有"},{"pid":"6b1cab5e49ff40c330a2dddba3dead14b4e88b2c","tid":309774,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n先秦兵器青銅為主，用鑄造而非鍛造，似乎唔係當時頂尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10104eaa7651686005e86b2136e54d84186ce599","tid":309774,"uid":118652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n先秦兵器青銅為主，用鑄造而非鍛造，似乎唔係當時頂尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳聞有一把劍係古怪咁架，好似有書本都有記載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287fb5f86551f0aeadeb0c5c8feace97a7b00f12","tid":309774,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:16:11.000Z","msg":"戰下手黎聽兵法"},{"pid":"60d7d5558002e7d1eff6fe2a22b4780fa3157383","tid":309774,"uid":118652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n先秦兵器青銅為主，用鑄造而非鍛造，似乎唔係當時頂尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳聞有一把劍係古怪咁架，好似有書本都有記載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thinkerstar.com/lu/essays/chin.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkerstar.com%2Flu%2Fessays%2Fchin.html&d=HllDwxlzWkFC1hx35qwS9AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=841e8aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thinkerstar.com/lu/essays/chin.html</a>"},{"pid":"1b82e381854d20ca5922205ac8c156642db53836","tid":309774,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"孫子兵法俾人吹得太大<br />\n講到萬能咁, 其實得啖笑<br />\n唐代李荃既太白陰經就正啦, 乜春都有. 以前我睇呢本"},{"pid":"15cc6aa22fa42ecdbc5d14aefcaa69a6ccde9f46","tid":309774,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"孫子兵法主要講治軍同戰略，比較小規模嘅戰術運用在六韜同孫臏兵法裡面就講得詳細得多。<br />\n<br />\n講史熟過兵法，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec42acb5193ed577385418c13c4e6ddf51aa32b9","tid":309774,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孫子兵法主要講治軍同戰略，比較小規模嘅戰術運用在六韜同孫臏兵法裡面就講得詳細得多。<br />\n<br />\n講史熟過兵法，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人唔鍾意睇問答類型（六韜），李衛公問對都一樣..<br />\nBtw, 春秋時代我反而推鬼谷子，佢d捭闔之術仲實用過乜春野職場孫子.."},{"pid":"c0f1d71170fc204515c55da6c80b05c5635b0966","tid":309774,"uid":60260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如d一排過既盾陣可以集中一點攻擊之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlm</blockquote><br />\n羅馬盾陣嗰種？我淨係讀過下明朝兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古中國軍事技藝唔及西方，好少有同一個作戰單位之中用相同武器嘅兵陣（例如西班牙長槍陣），多數係使用唔同武器嘅（例如戚繼光嘅鴛鴦陣）。</blockquote><br />\n盛唐陌刀陣，支那班學者吹到幾大下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8aea98a6924b4ea9886a862250a34bdbfb63003","tid":309774,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89c2a7193314970fd82bf1d43d7bd6ae2ace2e7","tid":309774,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n「兵者，詭道也」"},{"pid":"ede11f12145620155ad7bd8e61f2dbb8a8002442","tid":309774,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩開 total war medieval 2<br />\n最鐘意用重步+弩"},{"pid":"63d5e339af1cd6cd220cfeec3f58bb42aa156f33","tid":309774,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲步兵? 應該玩火槍?"},{"pid":"6e555410cecb7c8663d51e703c33b7ff7152be25","tid":309774,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b589ca46f98d6d3c0a5a56d0b5d02d9019150a","tid":309774,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇電影 講美國獨立戰爭個D 都好講究排陣"},{"pid":"66787703d7879a6b919957752d0e05c35fa44301","tid":309774,"uid":108922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"36e02eeac1c29d386e8f3c2bf023fa113739c723","tid":309774,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"請公子獻頭吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f257f422380a6009f4a4b0b59cf3c2f53264f8","tid":309774,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<br />\n但孫子兵法都唔係講佈陣<br />\n佢係講治國大戰略既基礎</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想知道方陣 矩陣果d點執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無聽過 馬其頓方陣<br />\n基本上 方陣係 砧板<br />\n騎兵係 錘仔 用黎夾死 d 步兵"},{"pid":"04645091d3d45cc970cf554130b597253677230d","tid":309774,"uid":61115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9SoWosg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9SoWosg.jpg&h=1a4b92f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孫子兵法咁算唔算講左戰術?"},{"pid":"8c7db883a6d76f499a1f0a050217b26532178fc1","tid":309774,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>孫子兵法主要講治軍同戰略，比較小規模嘅戰術運用在六韜同孫臏兵法裡面就講得詳細得多。<br />\n<br />\n講史熟過兵法，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人唔鍾意睇問答類型（六韜），李衛公問對都一樣..<br />\nBtw, 春秋時代我反而推鬼谷子，佢d捭闔之術仲實用過乜春野職場孫子..</blockquote><br />\n冇乜文學修為都睇唔明鬼谷子<br />\n又開又合又乾又濕都唔知佢講啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:師承鬼谷先生</span>"},{"pid":"a24596032e5b32cf9e4b364950df16cc835e233d","tid":309774,"uid":69662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"高質po 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0ab3dcf21a178c7f232bfb2843ed0c656e288b","tid":309774,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"之前係舊登開過po講歐洲古代戰陣<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6252679&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=True\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6252679%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DTrue&d=HllDwxlzWkFC1hx35qwS9AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=99c8c93b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6252679&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=True</a>"},{"pid":"ee80b2627cf1727c76dd8f42dccdb297f49d2e54","tid":309774,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>孫子兵法主要講治軍同戰略，比較小規模嘅戰術運用在六韜同孫臏兵法裡面就講得詳細得多。<br />\n<br />\n講史熟過兵法，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人唔鍾意睇問答類型（六韜），李衛公問對都一樣..<br />\nBtw, 春秋時代我反而推鬼谷子，佢d捭闔之術仲實用過乜春野職場孫子..</blockquote><br />\n冇乜文學修為都睇唔明鬼谷子<br />\n又開又合又乾又濕都唔知佢講啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:師承鬼谷先生</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺難睇,  寫得都幾有條理<br />\n先秦入面我最睇唔明既係戰國策, 一舊舊咁, 都唔知想寫D乜. 史又唔算, 兵書又唔算, 政書又唔算"},{"pid":"1a5c4d556895bae146f9abef693082922aacfad8","tid":309774,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9SoWosg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9SoWosg.jpg&h=1a4b92f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孫子兵法咁算唔算講左戰術?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D太正路<br />\n李世民用騎兵速攻取城, 完全偏離晒所有正路兵法(孫子)<br />\n呢D先學到野"},{"pid":"0bd20cf990e79a22324997df2230bca6bf6db66f","tid":309774,"uid":87557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>孫子兵法主要講治軍同戰略，比較小規模嘅戰術運用在六韜同孫臏兵法裡面就講得詳細得多。<br />\n<br />\n講史熟過兵法，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人唔鍾意睇問答類型（六韜），李衛公問對都一樣..<br />\nBtw, 春秋時代我反而推鬼谷子，佢d捭闔之術仲實用過乜春野職場孫子..</blockquote><br />\n冇乜文學修為都睇唔明鬼谷子<br />\n又開又合又乾又濕都唔知佢講啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:師承鬼谷先生</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺難睇,  寫得都幾有條理<br />\n先秦入面我最睇唔明既係戰國策, 一舊舊咁, 都唔知想寫D乜. 史又唔算, 兵書又唔算, 政書又唔算</blockquote><br />\n有條理還有條理，借代太亂、用字太深，我中文差睇到想撕書<br />\n反而我覺得戰國策又OK易睇，當單元故事睇毫無難度，只係啲道理冇畫出腸咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa282288d861b7ad114e2e61b0dc3ed836f7da8","tid":309774,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7ca531286156746100cc213fdbfc934896e198d5","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:43:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>孫子兵法主要講治軍同戰略，比較小規模嘅戰術運用在六韜同孫臏兵法裡面就講得詳細得多。<br />\n<br />\n講史熟過兵法，留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人唔鍾意睇問答類型（六韜），李衛公問對都一樣..<br />\nBtw, 春秋時代我反而推鬼谷子，佢d捭闔之術仲實用過乜春野職場孫子..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼谷子好似好難明 之前睇過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e4adc8978f103b7334d6980793db65dd09854d","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇電影 講美國獨立戰爭個D 都好講究排陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排隊打靶 有撚用"},{"pid":"8dad7eaa7f3b220d23dfb0859a3914acd962d392","tid":309774,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由 古代 到 現代 都用既 斜線陣，<br />\n揚長避短，集中優勢/火力 包圍。</blockquote><br />\n斜線陣（歷史之眼有講過）<br />\n<br />\n馬其頓 對 雅典 雙方都用斜線陣<br />\n<br />\n但馬其頓用騎兵隊 擾亂雅典個陣型（斷開）就立刻輸"},{"pid":"6267b6845e6ba3f34f90bb372d05f96d03fde18f","tid":309774,"uid":53103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇電影 講美國獨立戰爭個D 都好講究排陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排隊打靶 有撚用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小戰場係打靶姐，但係戰術層面嘅部隊調動係幾正<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rqe062l8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frqe062l8&h=3346ec38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab2a499dd71f2e1fa88d2f6a934e5cebfacf64d3","tid":309774,"uid":55300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"df2f3a7fc9ce9cb37226f5afe6cad86be7d2c463","tid":309774,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇電影 講美國獨立戰爭個D 都好講究排陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排隊打靶 有撚用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小戰場係打靶姐，但係戰術層面嘅部隊調動係幾正<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rqe062l8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frqe062l8&h=3346ec38&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n打完靶之後就白刃戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52f0bb9a17c0acd8f463e39a00c301d00f56879","tid":309774,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇電影 講美國獨立戰爭個D 都好講究排陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排隊打靶 有撚用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小戰場係打靶姐，但係戰術層面嘅部隊調動係幾正<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rqe062l8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frqe062l8&h=3346ec38&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n打完靶之後就白刃戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時衝鋒，向邊個方向衝鋒係戰術上都緊要既"},{"pid":"cedd3decd57c706c0bae7826a2618dffa9cff1d3","tid":309774,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"打機最基本兵法，騎克盾 盾克槍 槍克騎 弓用黎守城水戰戰術上部署唔可以太多"},{"pid":"295c7136e9d11a76cdf88cc70d2a11d30f0c1f62","tid":309774,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"無人講紀效新書    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bfa24caa3292cfc4a5689810bea303f1a9f30e","tid":309774,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n春秋唔係用銅劍嗎？同之後鋼劍技術差好多"},{"pid":"9faf3a05b9b072dbc6d903871d6793f299267e33","tid":309774,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n春秋唔係用銅劍嗎？同之後鋼劍技術差好多</blockquote><br />\n去到戰國尾 煉鐵技術先啱啱開始不過都早過西方"},{"pid":"d4f95c9c32f592230a618e16e24fef2b1f80a467","tid":309774,"uid":58998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n先秦兵器青銅為主，用鑄造而非鍛造，似乎唔係當時頂尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳聞有一把劍係古怪咁架，好似有書本都有記載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thinkerstar.com/lu/essays/chin.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkerstar.com%2Flu%2Fessays%2Fchin.html&d=HllDwxlzWkFC1hx35qwS9AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=841e8aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thinkerstar.com/lu/essays/chin.html</a></blockquote><br />\n支那文太高打飛機成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6efd3304eb70b58e00c4ecc03eee85b3b0b4b0","tid":309774,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法！"},{"pid":"237e9353ab05b5d111869ccfe76b13ce39ec67da","tid":309774,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑暗兵法！</blockquote><br />\n孫臏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n越王勾踐<br />\n<br />\n周文王"},{"pid":"6945cd267441176484a874f49259b09c42a15d55","tid":309774,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"d9fcf401c74321d11854bdad1e7537599545a6ca","tid":309774,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我淨係有興趣係18-19世紀西洋步兵戰術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實去到熱兵器之後嘅兵法都冇乜陣法可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇電影 講美國獨立戰爭個D 都好講究排陣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排隊打靶 有撚用</blockquote><br />\n火槍準繩度好差㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先要一排人一齊射"},{"pid":"538ed7f6b5a7604cf0d4feccd40461ead336ff9a","tid":309774,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n春秋唔係用銅劍嗎？同之後鋼劍技術差好多</blockquote><br />\n去到戰國尾 煉鐵技術先啱啱開始不過都早過西方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該係西方早過東亞"},{"pid":"ca686ea0e686b122cca409b02164c6b2a2412e21","tid":309774,"uid":53972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得孫子兵法似係心法咁，講既係高層次d既道理而無集中講實際操作<br />\n而事實隨住兵器，科技進步，戰爭方法都大有不同，好似以前既戰陣 去到而家飛彈年代作用已經無咁大，唯獨係用兵既心法唔會變，所以孫子兵法先咁受推崇<br />\n<br />\n用兵之法，非恃其不來，恃吾有以待也；非恃其不攻，恃吾有所不可攻也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583736a33401efe58bcbaed2bfc110c3c455ecd1","tid":309774,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"等睇高質po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9424b9d6ebf767250406954cd920defc6f49ccca","tid":309774,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而覺得孫子兵法似係心法咁，講既係高層次d既道理而無集中講實際操作<br />\n而事實隨住兵器，科技進步，戰爭方法都大有不同，好似以前既戰陣 去到而家飛彈年代作用已經無咁大，唯獨係用兵既心法唔會變，所以孫子兵法先咁受推崇<br />\n<br />\n用兵之法，非恃其不來，恃吾有以待也；非恃其不攻，恃吾有所不可攻也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兵貴神速！呢句心法歷久不衰。"},{"pid":"49a0780656a2d245cd799dfe9b3c763f907f1175","tid":309774,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"將苑?"},{"pid":"d9f6d1b4b442168d1602982d097dea9738310b74","tid":309774,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而覺得孫子兵法似係心法咁，講既係高層次d既道理而無集中講實際操作<br />\n而事實隨住兵器，科技進步，戰爭方法都大有不同，好似以前既戰陣 去到而家飛彈年代作用已經無咁大，唯獨係用兵既心法唔會變，所以孫子兵法先咁受推崇<br />\n<br />\n用兵之法，非恃其不來，恃吾有以待也；非恃其不攻，恃吾有所不可攻也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老美都係「不戰而屈人之兵，善之善者也」"},{"pid":"91f2d6d2a5cfca1deed3bdc669424a9de33e5277","tid":309774,"uid":1256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"長蛇陣係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31db0855e31109879bd020f995e7a09de03891c5","tid":309774,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇講兵馬俑有一把劍，埋在地下壓到曲左，拎黎上黎變番直，聽過乜q材料當年冇技術整到出黎，佢當兵法都數一數二</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n春秋唔係用銅劍嗎？同之後鋼劍技術差好多</blockquote><br />\n去到戰國尾 煉鐵技術先啱啱開始不過都早過西方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該係西方早過東亞</blockquote><br />\n如果西方計埋古埃及中東就係"},{"pid":"1daf028645dd5e0801479a898f16deb922c7d313","tid":309774,"uid":35538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩開 total war medieval 2<br />\n最鐘意用重步+弩</blockquote><br />\n英格蘭長弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74ebea63bd162fb0f632f1b7a7a507e15de1ad2","tid":309774,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長蛇陣係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行軍方式？<br />\n<br />\n拉到水蛇春咁長"}]}